The man went to hell after his death. They explained to him that every century the punishment would change and he was offered, at his discretion, to choose the first one. First, he was brought to punishment, where he was whipped. He refused. Then he was led to punishment, where some sinner was tortured with fire. He refused again. In the third punishment, a stunning blonde was giving a blowjob to an old man. The man naturally agreed. The devil came up to the blonde and said,
"That's enough for you! Come on, your torment is over!
